  "detailed_description": "Experience the thrill of teamwork and competition in Guns And Draguns, a roguelite shooting game. Navigate through a perilous fantasy dungeon, defeat enemies together, and gather upgrades to defeat the final boss. But don't trust your friends too much; you all aim to be the best player!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/1aade1473c84a66e6166508e72f0bf25.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/1aade1473c84a66e6166508e72f0bf25.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/1aade1473c84a66e6166508e72f0bf25.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Guns and Draguns is a cooperative top-down shooter game where you eliminate fantasy monsters with guns. To complete the game, you must finish all levels and defeat bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/69915e12f959637579ed9e9f8084ac20.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>With Remote Play Together, you can invite your Steam Friends to join your local co-op sessions remotely, without having to own or launch the game themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/ac28e9c4ad4449d2512aa911216d3699.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/ac28e9c4ad4449d2512aa911216d3699.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/ac28e9c4ad4449d2512aa911216d3699.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chests scattered in bonus or hidden rooms offer opportunities to enhance your abilities along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/8b33ed0585471a4bd361799ef7e53d16.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/8b33ed0585471a4bd361799ef7e53d16.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/8b33ed0585471a4bd361799ef7e53d16.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Success in this quest requires communication and cooperation with other players. You can play with up to 4 players, but you can also conquer the dungeon alone.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/4e7d560cdb9e3a655af1832a3faa64de.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/4e7d560cdb9e3a655af1832a3faa64de.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/4e7d560cdb9e3a655af1832a3faa64de.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Select one of the 7 unique characters available to defeat the Draguns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/33370fac60145c74083883222d8fb3d7.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/33370fac60145c74083883222d8fb3d7.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/33370fac60145c74083883222d8fb3d7.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>All teammates also compete to rank as the top player. Keys to this personal achievement include dealing damage, collecting coins, and being the ultimate bearer of the crown.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/5496492cce107074605f04a76e430ea9.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/5496492cce107074605f04a76e430ea9.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/5496492cce107074605f04a76e430ea9.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After each game, you can use the points earned to purchase new heroes, items, and game difficulties...",
  "about_the_game": "Experience the thrill of teamwork and competition in Guns And Draguns, a roguelite shooting game. Navigate through a perilous fantasy dungeon, defeat enemies together, and gather upgrades to defeat the final boss. But don't trust your friends too much; you all aim to be the best player!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/1aade1473c84a66e6166508e72f0bf25.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/1aade1473c84a66e6166508e72f0bf25.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/1aade1473c84a66e6166508e72f0bf25.mp4?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Guns and Draguns is a cooperative top-down shooter game where you eliminate fantasy monsters with guns. To complete the game, you must finish all levels and defeat bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/69915e12f959637579ed9e9f8084ac20.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>With Remote Play Together, you can invite your Steam Friends to join your local co-op sessions remotely, without having to own or launch the game themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/ac28e9c4ad4449d2512aa911216d3699.poster.avif?t=1737999076\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696390/extras/ac28e9c4ad4449d2512aa911216d3699.webm?t=1737999076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.